SIMPLE INSTRUCTIONS:

    TO RUN PLATFORMER:
    
        java -jar HW04_Server.jar 0
        java -jar HW04_Client.jar 0
    
    TO RUN BUBBLE SHOOTER:
    
        java -jar HW04_Server.jar 1
        java -jar HW04_Client.jar 1
    
    TO RUN SPACE INVADERS:

        java -jar HW04_Server.jar 2
        java -jar HW04_Client.jar 2

MORE DETAILS:

    TO COMPILE:
    
        Manually
    
            javac -classpath .:./core.jar HW04_Server.java
            javac -classpath .:./core.jar HW04_Client.java
        
        Using Bash Script
        
            ./HW04_Recompile
            
    TO CREATE JAR FILES (AFTER COMPILING):
    
        jar cvfm HW04_Server.jar HW04_Server.mf *.class core.jar
        jar cvfm HW04_Client.jar HW04_Client.mf *.class core.jar
    
    TO RUN SERVER:
    
        Manually
    
            java -classpath .:./core.jar HW04_Server [game: 0 platformer, 1 bubble shooter, 2 space invaders]
        
        Using Bash Script
        
            ./HW04_RunServer [game: 0 platformer, 1 bubble shooter, 2 space invaders]
            
        Using JAR
        
            java -jar HW04_Server.jar [game: 0 platformer, 1 bubble shooter, 2 space invaders]
        
    TO RUN CLIENT:
    
        Manually
    
            java -classpath .:./core.jar HW04_Client [game: 0 platformer, 1 bubble shooter, 2 space invaders]
        
        Using Bash Script
        
            ./HW04_RunClient [game: 0 platformer, 1 bubble shooter, 2 space invaders]
            
        Using JAR
        
            java -jar HW04_Client.jar [game: 0 platformer, 1 bubble shooter, 2 space invaders]

